title: BEUTIFUL CENTENNIAL LAKES CONDOMINIUM
posting_body: ['Renting my condo starting from December.', 'Light furnished option available.', 'This condo is in one of the best areas of centennial lakes.', 'The trail is right across my unit.', 'The laundry room is right next to my unit and the trash room is 2 doors down the hallway.', 'The unit is super clean and occupied by only one person for many years.', 'Other features', 'Restaurants - walking distance', 'YMCA Gym - across the street.', 'Grocery stores (Byerlys, Whole Foods, Trader Joes) - all less than a mile.', 'Hospitals, clinics, drug stores - all less than a mile.', 'Target - 0.5 miles', 'Southdale mall - 0.9 miles', 'MSP international airport - 12 minutes drive', 'Mall of America and Ikea - 8 minutes drive', 'Nearby Parks - Centennial Lakes, Roseland Park, Arden Park, Woodland Lake Nature Center, East Bush Lake Beach.', 'Must sign a one year lease.', 'Must have strong work history or source of funds and provide 2 references.', "No pets and no grilling per condo's policies.", "There's an outdoor pool and grill.", 'Water, trash, cable, and heat is paid.', 'My bill in the summer averages to $40.', 'One underground heated car garage space.', 'I can easily fit my motorcycle and a car.', "There's also an option for you to build a storage space in front of the garage space or put your bikes.", 'You have one storage space inside the unit too with plenty of room for household items and totes.', 'The location is excellent to get to Minneapolis or other nearby cities in the south.', 'Building is two level.', 'This is the lower level unit and people here are very quiet and respectful.', 'No elevator so you have to take the stairs after you park your car in the garage or you could park right outside the unit and access the unit through the patio door with lock.', 'Also, there are two main entry doors on either side.', 'The unit was recently remodeled.', 'Newer hardwood floor and toilet.', 'In the process to add Kohler pro inspired sink kit and do other upgrades before renting.', "There's a also a spacious and covered patio space.", 'Mini golf, weekly farmers market, events, art festival, and more at Centennial Lakes.', 'This is one of the best places to go for daily walks.', 'If you need to rent sooner then let me know.', 'Please call or text me if you are interested.']
